history.content: See @5830, similar problem with a different class. I think your best bet would be to contact the CalCentral team.

When I tried to change the discussion session time for EE16B (new dis. session was open), even though the system said that the change was successful, my old discussion session was dropped from the schedule without the new discussion session added (strangely, I was still enrolled in both lecture and lab). Thus, I had to drop the class and reenroll immediately to solve this problem. Is this a bug in the system?
